[30;1m3441 | [0m[35m        Executes traceroute on the device and returns a dictionary with the result.[0m
[30;1m3442 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m3443 | [0m[35m        :param destination: Host or IP Address of the destination[0m
[30;1m3444 | [0m[35m        :param source: Use a specific IP Address to execute the traceroute[0m
[30;1m3445 | [0m[35m        :type source: optional[0m
